description:
We are seeking individuals who are forward thinking, visionaries with a strong work, ethic, self-motivated with a strong commitment to creating their own life their way via an independent contracting role.

Please take note that candidates must have at least 5 years’ of work experience to be considered.

Are you ready and willing to transfer your existing skillset and talents across to establishing an independent enterprise of your own?

We offer a ‘plug and play’, turnkey solution complete with ongoing training, robust support platforms, with a full suite of world-class and award-winning personal development products.

Have you been considering working for yourself as an independent contractor for a while and feel that now is your time? Are you looking for time freedom, portability and flexibility to craft your own workspace from wherever you choose to be with only your laptop and phone?

Our opportunity offers all of these and so much more. Profits are from the sale of products so you will be comfortable in a sales environment. The ability to earn up to $8,000 per sale is very possible here.

With a global demand for our Personal Development products, we are actively seeking ambitious and big thinking professionals ready to embark on a new journey of self-growth and business success.

We’re looking for creative, out of the box thinkers to infuse a new perspective into our team.

We’re looking for team players – those willing to contribute to an already vibrant global group creating real change in the world.

Would you describe yourself as a bit different? Someone who goes against the grain, stands out from the crowd, a professional who thinks very differently to the ‘herd’? If so, then we want to talk to you.

Responsibilities:

Carry out daily interviews to qualify prospects to receive our biz information.

Devote time daily to our suite of personal development products.

Actively attend and participate in our weekly Zoom training calls.

Market our in-demand products across varied advertising platforms.

Maintain a consistent positive attitude.

What We Are Looking For From You:

· You are someone who takes pride in their work;

· You are driven to succeed;

· You would describe yourself as ambitious;

· You are ready to step into the best version of you;

· You are energetic;

· You are coachable and trainable;

· You are highly motivated;

· You possess strong interpersonal communication skills;

· You speak professional English or are a native speaker;

· You are collaborative;

· You are resourceful;

· You are goal-oriented and focussed;

· You are an independent professional and show initiative and strong problem solving skills;

· You have a strong desire to lift others up and grow an organization.

We currently operate in over 130 countries around the world.

Our products are life transforming online courses and live events in the personal development and leadership development sector so these would both be passion projects for you.

If your application is successful, we will be in touch by phone for a brief 5 – 10 minute interview.

Not at all suited to those seeking a work VISA or students.
